text: Jakobína Jakobsdóttir (born 21 November 1932) is an Icelandic alpine skier. She competed in three events at the 1956 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1932 births Category:Living people Category:Icelandic female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Iceland Category:Alpine skiers at the 1956 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Reykjavík
